The Executive 15 from the Werks Professional™ Collection by Victorinox Travel Gear is a stylish expandable laptop case that features and iPad or tablet compartment. It is the ideal business case for a busy agenda.
asset.author: Victorinox AG

transcripts: The executive 15 is the perfect brief for the professional seeking a traditional silhouette with modern style. Inside the case you will find padded storage for up to a 15.6 inch or forty centimeter laptop and a dedicated tablet pocket. There is also plenty of room for your essential cords and accessories. Lockable by KK super sliders on the main compartment allow you to keep your valuable electronics protected. The front organizational panel contains multi-purpose pockets. Ideal for a mobile phone, USB flash drives, business cards and more. For quick access items you will find a flap over pocket on the exterior of the back. The back features 2 inch or five centimeters separate expansion to provide additional capacity. And a multi-purpose stretch side pocket holds a water bottle or an umbrella. The rear pocket and zips allowing the case to slide over the handle system of wheeled luggage so you can travel easily but multiple bags. A padded all handle and a removable adjustable shoulder strap delivers superior comfort.
